401
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:05,290
I'm not afraid to tell you the truth.

402
00:23:06,410 --> 00:23:08,530
I don't want those useless pieces of paper

403
00:23:08,530 --> 00:23:09,740
from Japan either.

404
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:11,440
But if the cost is losing

405
00:23:11,470 --> 00:23:14,270
France's concession rights in Shanghai,

406
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:15,610
