409
00:23:18,750 --> 00:23:20,950
we Chinese are the ones being extorted.

410
00:23:21,580 --> 00:23:23,240
We have an old saying in China:

411
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:24,570
"Being generous with other people's money."

412
00:23:24,570 --> 00:23:25,400
Mr. Frank,

413
00:23:25,950 --> 00:23:28,050
