414
00:23:28,050 --> 00:23:28,820
Hongsheng,

415
00:23:28,890 --> 00:23:29,970
let me remind you.

416
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:32,990
You are working for the French Republic,

417
00:23:33,210 --> 00:23:34,810
and like your father,

418
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:35,610
you must

419
00:23:35,630 --> 00:23:37,700
always prioritize its highest interests

420
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:38,860
in everything.

421
00:23:40,690 --> 00:23:41,770
Mr. Frank,

422
00:23:42,100 --> 00:23:43,300
with all due respect,

423
00:23:43,530 --> 00:23:44,730
I am Chinese.

424
00:23:46,060 --> 00:23:47,380
My first priority

425
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:50,740
will always be the interests of the Chinese people.

426
00:24:06,820 --> 00:24:08,020
Mr. Yun, you're back.

427
00:24:10,300 --> 00:24:11,980
You two, come to my study.

428
00:24:12,250 --> 00:24:12,890
Shen,

429
00:24:13,430 --> 00:24:14,270
wait here.

430
00:24:35,060 --> 00:24:35,540
Dad,

431
00:24:36,660 --> 00:24:38,290
