432
00:24:38,290 --> 00:24:39,960
Are you still Chinese?

433
00:24:41,250 --> 00:24:42,980
Do you remember what you told me

434
00:24:44,060 --> 00:24:45,820
when you decided to go to France to study finance?

435
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,340
Mr. Zhang Si once said,

436
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:48,970
"Among the best ways to save the country,

437
00:24:48,970 --> 00:24:50,700
education is like flowers, while the army and navy are like fruits.

438
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:52,400
But the foundation lies in industry."

439
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,510
So, I've made up my mind

440
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:54,500
to study finance

441
00:24:54,730 --> 00:24:57,360
and pursue the path of saving the country through industry in the future.

442
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:57,970
But later,

443
00:24:58,320 --> 00:25:00,920
you dropped out and came to Shanghai to find me.

444
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:01,780
Why?

445
00:25:02,760 --> 00:25:03,190
Dad,

446
00:25:03,730 --> 00:25:04,860
given the current situation,

447
00:25:04,860 --> 00:25:06,700
industry alone can no longer save China.

448
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:09,070
Winning this war is the urgent priority.

449
00:25:09,540 --> 00:25:10,790
Please stop telling me about that

450
00:25:10,790 --> 00:25:12,650
"more friends means more paths."

451
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:13,860
The French

452
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,460
will never truly be our friends.

453
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:17,860
I just want an honest answer from you today.

454
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:19,970
If we're on different paths...

455
00:25:19,970 --> 00:25:20,770
What then?

456
00:25:22,810 --> 00:25:24,270
Then we can only part ways.

457
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:26,240
Alright, I see you're determined.

458
00:25:26,290 --> 00:25:28,020
Before I answer your question,

459
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:29,350
could you explain

460
00:25:29,370 --> 00:25:30,690
your series of

461
00:25:30,730 --> 00:25:32,770
foolish and reckless actions today?

462
00:25:32,770 --> 00:25:35,500
The reason I got involved with the NBIS's business

463
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:38,020
is simply because Chinese people should help fellow Chinese,

464
00:25:38,020 --> 00:25:40,510
even if there are many things they've done that I disapprove of.

465
00:25:40,510 --> 00:25:42,010
