471
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:50,720
Let me tell you.

472
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:52,200
You've already been exposed,

473
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:53,350
including me.

474
00:25:58,820 --> 00:25:59,450
I don't know

475
00:25:59,450 --> 00:26:01,490
