477
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:06,760
This is too passive.

478
00:26:07,410 --> 00:26:09,210
I don't like this feeling at all.

479
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:10,310
I've actually

480
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:12,050
let such a formidable enemy

481
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:14,550
spy on me unchecked for so long.

482
00:26:16,940 --> 00:26:19,870
This is the biggest disgrace of my career as an agent.

483
00:26:20,250 --> 00:26:21,310
Sorry, Mr. Tanaka.

484
00:26:21,820 --> 00:26:23,820
It was my fault for being negligent.

485
00:26:23,970 --> 00:26:25,970
