495
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:49,320
Such beautiful sunlight,

496
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:53,220
yet you'll never see it again.

497
00:26:54,410 --> 00:26:55,290
Impossible.

498
00:26:55,500 --> 00:26:57,390
I'm quite certain that they didn't discover me.

499
