505
00:27:07,090 --> 00:27:08,690
Don't you find that strange?

506
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:12,570
If you had only helped the NBIS

507
00:27:12,570 --> 00:27:13,680
at the train station

508
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:15,480
without preventing Viscount from meeting them,

509
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,180
