514
00:27:24,490 --> 00:27:25,430
You acted on your own,

515
00:27:25,430 --> 00:27:26,890
being so self-righteous,

516
00:27:26,930 --> 00:27:29,330
and tried to stop Viscount from meeting them.

517
00:27:29,330 --> 00:27:31,080
Do you think you succeeded in this?

518
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:32,260
Well, let me tell you,

519
00:27:32,260 --> 00:27:33,980
Viscount set a trap,

520
00:27:34,010 --> 00:27:35,610
